<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-10 px-4 pb-20 transition-colors duration-300">
  
  <header class="text-center mb-12">
    <div class="inline-block p-3 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 rounded-2xl mb-4 transition-colors">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 005.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-400 mb-4 transition-colors">Rede de Apoio e Orientações</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto transition-colors">Você não está sozinho(a). Existem profissionais e instituições preparados para auxiliar no desenvolvimento do seu filho.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="mb-12 bg-linear-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 dark:from-blue-900 dark:to-gray-900 rounded-3xl p-8 text-white shadow-xl shadow-blue-200 dark:shadow-none border border-transparent dark:border-blue-800/50 transition-colors duration-300">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="bg-blue-500 dark:bg-blue-800 p-1 rounded-lg">🚀</span> Primeiros Passos Recomendados
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white/10 dark:bg-black/20 p-4 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-transparent dark:border-white/5 transition-colors">
        <span class="text-2xl font-bold block mb-2 text-blue-50 dark:text-blue-300">01</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-1 text-blue-100 dark:text-white">Mantenha a Calma</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-blue-50 dark:text-gray-300 opacity-90 leading-relaxed">Cada criança tem seu ritmo. Um marco atrasado é apenas um sinal para observação, não um diagnóstico definitivo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/10 dark:bg-black/20 p-4 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-transparent dark:border-white/5 transition-colors">
        <span class="text-2xl font-bold block mb-2 text-blue-50 dark:text-blue-300">02</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-1 text-blue-100 dark:text-white">Gere o Relatório</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-blue-50 dark:text-gray-300 opacity-90 leading-relaxed">Use a função "Gerar Relatório Médico" deste app para levar os dados anotados e facilitar a conversa com o profissional.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/10 dark:bg-black/20 p-4 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-transparent dark:border-white/5 transition-colors">
        <span class="text-2xl font-bold block mb-2 text-blue-50 dark:text-blue-300">03</span>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-1 text-blue-100 dark:text-white">Agende Pediatra</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-blue-50 dark:text-gray-300 opacity-90 leading-relaxed">O pediatra é o profissional capacitado para avaliar se há necessidade de encaminhamento para especialistas.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <div class="p-2 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/40 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 rounded-xl transition-colors">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 transition-colors">Telefones e Emergência</h3>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl transition-colors">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase transition-colors">Disque Saúde</p>
            <p class="font-black text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-400 transition-colors">136</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 px-2 py-1 rounded-full border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 transition-colors">SUS</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl transition-colors">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase transition-colors">SAMU</p>
            <p class="font-black text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-400 transition-colors">192</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 px-2 py-1 rounded-full border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 transition-colors">Emergência</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <div class="p-2 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/40 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 rounded-xl transition-colors">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 transition-colors">Portais e Comunidades</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <%= link_to "https://www.gov.br/saude/pt-br/assuntos/saude-da-crianca", target: "_blank", class: "flex items-center justify-between p-3 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 rounded-2xl hover:bg-purple-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors" do %>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Saúde da Criança (Gov)</span>
          <span class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 transition-colors">→</span>
        <% end %>
        <%= link_to "https://www.movimentodown.org.br/", target: "_blank", class: "flex items-center justify-between p-3 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 rounded-2xl hover:bg-purple-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors" do %>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Movimento Down</span>
          <span class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 transition-colors">→</span>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="mt-12 text-center transition-colors">
    <%= link_to "Voltar ao Início", root_path, class: "text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 font-bold text-sm transition-colors" %>
  </footer>
</div>